creator: Recloak
descriptionHtml:
Little Alchemy, the crafting game enjoyed by millions of players, is back with more items, fresh, new art style and charming music!

Mix items and create the world from scratch! Discover exciting items accompanied by funny descriptions and lose yourself exploring the huge, new library!

Little Alchemy 2 features:
A completely new library.
Vibrant art style.
Original soundtrack.
Encyclopedia with cool item descriptions.

What are you waiting for? A whole world is waiting to be discovered!
descriptionShort: Mix items and discover exciting combinations! Little Alchemy returns in style!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fixed a bug causing the game to close when pressing back button while the encyclopedia window was opened.
Fixed a bug preventing the game from loading on some devices using Android 6.0 and lower.
Fixed animations on some devices using Android 5.1.
